OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight frost and fog
OL,6,Fwill soon clear to leave plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine to start with on Sunday.
OL,8,FCloud will slowly bubble up during the
OL,9,Fmorning, with one of two light showers
OL,10,Fdeveloping this afternoon. Lighter
OL,11,Fwinds than recently.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe odd shower is possible
OL,14,Fthis evening, but a dry night is
OL,15,Fexpected with clear spells. A slight
OL,16,Ffrost forming in rural areas. Some
OL,17,Fcloud arriving in the east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
