OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FEarly sunshine will give way
OL,6,Fto an increase in cloud from the east
OL,7,Fon Monday. Perhaps a few showers
OL,8,Farriving later. A slight easterly
OL,9,Fbreeze developing, though feeling
OL,10,Fpleasant enough.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FTuesday will start rather cloudy with
OL,14,Fsome showers, though brightening up
OL,15,Flater. Dry with some sunshine on
OL,16,FWednesday and Thursday, though a brisk
OL,17,Fwind developing, making it feel rather
OL,18,Fcool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
